</p>
            <p>相反詞：<span style="font-family:Verdana,Helvetica,Arial; font-style:normal; font-variant:normal; font-weight:normal; color:rgb(17,17,17); word-spacing:0px; letter-spacing:normal; text-transform:none; text-indent:0px; line-height:19.2019px; float:none;">人去樓空</span></p>
